wholesalecustomers

Tahani AlHarbi

11/19/2020

Description:

here I would analyze data about wholesales customers and answer some questions about annual spending of products in these Regions

data:

The dataset refers to clients of a wholesale distributor. It includes the annual spending in monetary units (m.u.) on diverse product categories channel 1 Horeca channel 2 Retail
regions: Lisbon, Porto and other region

Attribute Information:

  • FRESH: annual spending (m.u.) on fresh products (Continuous);

  • MILK: annual spending (m.u.) on milk products (Continuous);

  • GROCERY: annual spending (m.u.)on grocery products (Continuous);

  • FROZEN: annual spending (m.u.)on frozen products (Continuous)

  • DETERGENTS_PAPER: annual spending (m.u.) on detergents and products (Continuous)

  • DELICATESSEN: annual spending (m.u.)on and delicatessen products (Continuous);

  • CHANNEL: customers Channel - Horeca (Hotel/Restaurant/Cafe) or Retail channel (Nominal)

  • REGION: customers Region Lisnon, Oporto or Other (Nominal)
